{"tid":1362131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭成功第三黃金規則詳解 - Be Water (中）資訊處理","createTime":"2019-07-24T19:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:45:14.000Z","uid":86509,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"436f905a4c0e0ca7f54b1cd109be82d2f3b00334","tid":1362131,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:10:33.000Z","msg":"三大規則<br />\n<br />\n一、團結<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310533\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310533</a><br />\n<br />\n二、敵反我擁；敵擁我反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321275\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321275</a><br />\n<br />\n三、Be Water<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329077\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329077</a><br />\n<br />\n上集講咗Be Water意思係<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">變成無形 再 靈活變通</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n變成無形就講咗啦<br />\n就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">破除思想框架</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但點靈活變通？<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講就係<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>因敵制勝</strong></span><br />\n嫌多字可以正皮出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n複雜嚟講就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>建立靈活機制應付事物<br />\n良好嘅資訊處理<br />\n且從現實中不斷驗證呢套機制</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>資訊處理</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所謂資訊處理就係風險管理<br />\n愈搜集資料不效率風險愈高<br />\n愈易做錯決定<br />\n後果都愈嚴重<br />\n<br />\n而要處理資訊首先要一個目的<br />\n因為冇目的處理資訊係無意思嘅<br />\nBe Water 目的<strong>必應為協助對人事物判斷</strong><br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n我目的係計劃727元朗遊行行動<br />\n<br />\n注意返處理資訊時有四點要注意<br />\n<br />\n1.勿被引起情緒 、情緒理應係工具係要主動引起<br />\n例：廣告、&ldquo;飯民又篤灰&rdquo;<br />\n2.勿直接行動跟大隊，而未經獨立思考判斷<br />\n3.勿被轉移視線 <br />\n4.勿就咁信咗 <br />\n例如：就咁&ldquo;fact checked&quot;&quot;confirmed&quot;&quot;一手料&rdquo;&ldquo;極可信消息&rdquo;&ldquo;已證實&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就會將資訊處理分三個part<br />\n一、搜集資訊<br />\n二、過濾資訊<br />\n三、分析資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一、搜集資訊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>睇標題、keywords（例如粗體嘅字）</strong><br />\n判斷係咪與目的相關資訊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>要學識速讀</strong><br />\n唔好係個腦逐字讀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>搵資料嘅方法</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最佳辦法：等資料搵你</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實係好主觀<br />\n我自己就訂閱呢啲<br />\n你都可以建立屬於自己嘅資料源<br />\n貴精不貴多<br />\n<br />\nFact Check:<br />\n求驗傳媒 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkauyim%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=3d3524f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/</a><br />\n <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFKLi0fTZiWg0bGwjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFKLi0fTZiWg0bGwjA&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=47c4b04f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFKLi0fTZiWg0bGwjA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFKLi0fTZiWg0bGwjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFKLi0fTZiWg0bGwjA&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=47c4b04f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFKLi0fTZiWg0bGwjA</a><br />\n<br />\n連登：我要攬炒、高學歷廢青、月娥奔中、鍵盤戰團<br />\nfacebook：蘋果、立場、Now、有線<br />\n陶傑、Chenglap、李懂媽<br />\nYoutube：志森與志豪 、RTHK（尤其視點31）<br />\nInstagram：老了唔太識<br />\n<br />\n避免同溫層效應<br />\n我都會睇<br />\n幫港出聲、HKG報、港人講地、o嘴網<br />\n睇下佢哋接收咗咩錯誤訊息<br />\n但大家留意下呢啲網有洗腦訊息<br />\n記緊記勿信當中任何訊息，佢哋係唔會做任何fact check同特登放假資料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>趕時間辦法：問/討論</strong></span></span><br />\n搵啲有經驗可信嘅人，<br />\n以集體智慧搜集資料以便決策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有時間辦法：</span></span></strong><br />\n連登：除熱門，都去時事台睇一睇，善用搜尋<br />\nTelegram：係連登搵/問戰友拎<br />\ngoogle：搜尋技巧<a href=\"https://transbiz.com.tw/google%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B-search-tips/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransbiz.com.tw%2Fgoogle%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%25B0%258B-search-tips%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=1659ec56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transbiz.com.tw/google%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B-search-tips/</a><br />\n善用圖片搜尋<br />\n轉換關鍵字，可以搵更準確資料，專業知識轉英文搜尋更佳<br />\n蘋果動新聞<br />\n其他：Facebook、youtube、Instagram、wiki...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>觀察驗證</strong></span></span><br />\n當然可以親身觀察驗證<br />\n搜集第一身資訊<br />\n<strong>觀察就建議將事物整體觀察同分部份觀察</strong><br />\n<br />\n例如：觀察警察可分為行為、裝備、人數、位置<br />\n<br />\n<strong>驗證你學咗知識</strong><br />\n例如：中椒食蛋聽人講用茶洗好啲<br />\n你可親身試下係咪真<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">二、過濾資訊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n問自己兩個問題<br />\n<strong>重要？ 同 可信？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">①重要？</span></span></strong><br />\n唔重要&rarr;緊係唔睇啦大佬<br />\n重要&rarr;<br />\n要學識搵Key Information<br />\n唔好乜都睇<br />\n重要嘅睇先，細心啲讀<br />\n次重要得閒先睇，快速閱讀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>②可信？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家要有懷疑精神<br />\n請凡事懷疑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Fact Check？</strong></span></span><br />\n我發現大家都誤解咗Fact Check 係乜<br />\n坊間嘅Fact Check 意思其實係 Trust Check<br />\n&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;<br />\nTrust Check 唔可以用 Fact Check 字眼<br />\n&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;<br />\n<em></em><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Trust check ：<br />\n多個可信source 發佈同一資訊，而冇不一致成份<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n單一source就過唔到Trust Check <br />\n其實我寫呢篇嘢咁啱發生 明報冇大肚婆事件<br />\n我當時係少數冇炒車連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁咩叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>可信source</em></span></strong></span>呢？<br />\n<br />\n1.Where?=Source?<br />\n避免 有分化撚 斷章取義、誤導遺漏甚至修改內容<br />\n最好 睇原文<br />\n2.Who?=起底<br />\n立場？專業？權威？身份？過往表現？<br />\n3.What?=目的？<br />\n邊個係真正讀者？（換位思考） 想你做咩？<br />\n例如：致年青人條片講父母唔愛你，咁唔合理<br />\n目的係想年青人同父母斷絕關係咩？<br />\n正路應該係致父母 等父母明白了解我哋至啱<br />\n4.When?<br />\nOutdated?未發生？<br />\n剛發生？（未經時間考驗可信性都較低）<br />\n5.一致性？<br />\n有冇前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;<br />\n請勿 睇正負皮、訴諸權威、因人廢言<br />\n&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果做唔到trust check <br />\n但你又覺得好重要</strong><br />\n匿名報料/錄音報料/whatsapp 圖 就寫流傳<br />\n緊急啲 就寫流傳求證<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">真&bull;Fact Check</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>自己親身驗証過資料正確<br />\n問過當事人證實，而當事人係可信</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外<strong><em><span style=\"color: gold;\">親身經歷</span></em></strong>唔係講&ldquo;Fact Check&rdquo;<br />\n係用親身經歷、一手料、直播見到<br />\n唔肯定就加&ldquo;求證&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寫住咁多先<br />\n唔睇打撚死你哋班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbetween點解放學術台呢<br />\n因為時事台係痴線咁多post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bda27454189ceed2d0ff6deb9a2b77cf348ecfd","tid":1362131,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:11:39.000Z","msg":"參考咗巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[基本功] 教大家咩叫 FACT CHECK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357480</a>"},{"pid":"63b56b88c70c83c9b085b673ce39fc17f0eee5cd","tid":1362131,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:12:43.000Z","msg":"其實一早係諗住寫fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話心血來潮去寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd4d2cefd84579070f2d7c3a31cdce4db49ff0e","tid":1362131,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6dc5850d80fd28290fc1998c5b0e6a84309cad","tid":1362131,"uid":67292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:13:22.000Z","msg":"咁夜先開，但都幫你推！"},{"pid":"ca9d311fd1a3c7b0b6e10487f8941242455f805f","tid":1362131,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f6dc5850d80fd28290fc1998c5b0e6a84309cad","tid":1362131,"uid":67292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:13:22.000Z","msg":"咁夜先開，但都幫你推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fe0393dbfa4b29811092305f0f01d7565eb00b","tid":1362131,"uid":283465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:15:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c025a25b722c9eddd41ee07485b6cdb240